<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If you give the static method Zend_Text_MultiByte::wordWrap a string that has the same length as the maximum length for a line plus an ending space and set the cut parameter to true, the ending space will be added to the first line and no second line is created.</p>

<p>For example</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$text = 'aloha ';
echo Zend_Text_MultiByte::wordWrap($text, 5, '-', true);
</code></pre>

<p>returns 'aloha ' but should return 'aloha-'</p>

